name: Rock Vibe
blurb: Rock Vibe makes it possible for people who are blind or sighted to play a Rock Band-like game on their PCs or Macs.

rewards.reward: The satisfaction of knowing how awesome you are!! Also, you can access all of the project updates here on Kickstarter + get the Keeping Time application download that helps you keep track of time while you're on your computer.
